## Data Flow

### Synchronous Flow

```
Client Request
    ↓
[Rate Limiter Check]
    ↓ (Pass)
[API Key Validation]
    ↓ (Valid)
[Request Validation]
    ↓ (Valid)
[Email Sanitization]
    ↓
[Circuit Breaker Check]
    ↓ (CLOSED)
[SMTP Send - Attempt 1]
    ↓ (Success)
[Log Success Metrics]
    ↓
Return 200 OK Response
```

### Asynchronous Flow

```
Client Request
    ↓
[Rate Limiter Check]
    ↓ (Pass)
[API Key Validation]
    ↓ (Valid)
[Request Validation]
    ↓ (Valid)
[Submit to Thread Pool]
    ↓
Return 202 Accepted (Immediate)
    │
    └─→ [Background Processing]
            ↓
        [Email Sanitization]
            ↓
        [Circuit Breaker Check]
            ↓ (CLOSED)
        [SMTP Send - Attempt 1]
            ↓ (Fail)
        [Wait 2s - Retry Attempt 2]
            ↓ (Fail)
        [Wait 4s - Retry Attempt 3]
            ↓ (Fail)
        [Send to Dead Letter Queue]
            ↓
        [Log Failure Metrics]
```

### Failover Flow

```
[Primary SMTP Send]
    ↓ (Connection Timeout)
[Circuit Breaker Opens]
    ↓
[Switch to Backup SMTP]
    ↓
[Backup SMTP Send]
    ↓ (Success)
[Log Failover Event]
    ↓
[Alert Operations Team]
```

